title: 30 MIN KILLER STRENGTH Workout - With Weights - Home Workout with Dumbbells
description:
Hey Team, a new 30 min KILLER STRENGTH workout with dumbbells! The focus is on toning and strengthening your full body with this home workout. Grab your Dumbbells and let's do this! Let's go!

♡📱 Sign up to my Grow with Anna APP for more workouts & challenges: https://growwithanna.com?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=launch

▸ Level: Intermediate
▸ Time: 30 Min
▸ Equipment: 2x 5kg and 2x 8kg Dumbbells

Workout:
▸ Warm Up + Mobility 45 sec on, no rest
▸ Full Body Burn 30 sec on, no rest
▸ Upper Body Finisher 60 sec on, no rest
▸ Lower Body Finisher 60 sec on, no rest
▸ Cool Down 30 sec on, 10 sec off

Please remember that we are all different and that you can make this your own workout ♡ Take a longer break when you need to.
